basics.summary:
I am a PhD student co-supervised by [Véronique Bruyère](http://informatique.umons.ac.be/perso/Bruyere.Veronique/) from the Computer Science department at the [University of Mons (UMONS)](https://web.umons.ac.be) and by [Guillermo A. Perez](https://www.uantwerpen.be/en/staff/guillermoalberto-perez/) from the Computer Science department at the [University of Antwerp (UAntwerpen)](https://www.uantwerpen.be/en/). My PhD Thesis started in October 2020 and is funded by the [F.R.S.-FNRS](https://www.frs-fnrs.be/en/). My research interests include
 * One-counter automata learning;
 * Formal verification, using automata.
